{"article_id":"SL8uZcnb7IZo1v2I","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Outgoing president says","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"US will respond to cyberattacks by Moscow ' at a time and place of our choosing ' ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"as Donald Trump rejects reports of interference","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Barack Obama has warned","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that the US will retaliate for Russian cyberattacks during the presidential election .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"In an interview on National Public Radio on Friday morning , the US president said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"he is waiting for a final report","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"he has ordered","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"into a range of Russian hacking attacks ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"but promised","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"there would be a response .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"White House press secretary says","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Putin had direct role","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"in hacking US election","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Read more","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"there is no doubt","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"when any foreign government tries to impact the integrity of our elections ...","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"we need to take action , \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"Obama said .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" And we will - at a time and place of our own choosing . \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Some of it may be explicit and publicised ;","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"some of it may not be . \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"The CIA has judged","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that the Russian cyber attacks ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"including the hacking of emails from the Democratic National Committee ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"were intended to influence the election in Donald Trump ' s favour ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"according to reports .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The FBI agrees","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that there was Russian hacking","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"but has not as yet concluded","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"it was intended to favour the Republican contender .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Senators from both parties have called for a congressional enquiry ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"while Trump himself has rejected the reports","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and his office has derided the CIA .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Trump weighed in on Twitter","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"to ask","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"if it was the \" same cyberattack","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"where it was revealed that head of the DNC illegally gave Hillary the questions to the debate ? \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"One of the hacked emails , from interim DNC head Donna Brazile , said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that a woman from Flint , Michigan , would ask at a primary debate with Bernie Sanders what Clinton would do as president","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to help people in the town","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"suffering from a lead-contaminated water supply .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Are we talking about the same cyberattack","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"where it was revealed that head of the DNC illegally gave Hillary the questions to the debate ?","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"He earlier tweeted :","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"\" If Russia , or some other entity , was hacking ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"why did the White House wait so long","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"to act ?","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Why did they only complain","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"after Hillary lost ? \"","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"In fact , the intelligence community had issued its statement on 7 October , a full month before polling day .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Obama said","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"he would reserve judgment on Moscow ' s intentions","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"pending a final report","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"but he said","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"the impact of the intervention was clear .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"The debate over motivation ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"\" does not in any way ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"I think ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"detract from the basic point","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"that everyone during the election perceived accurately -","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"that in fact what the Russian hack had done was create more problems for the Clinton campaign","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"than it had for the Trump campaign \" .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"\" There ' s no doubt","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that it contributed to an atmosphere","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"in which the only focus for weeks at a time , months at a time were Hillary ' s emails , the Clinton Foundation , political gossip surrounding the DNC . \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"The president did not attempt to gauge the full impact of the intervention ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"but insisted","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"it had had an effect .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Trump ' s relationship with Russia - what we know and what comes next","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"\" Elections can always turn out differently , \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"\" You never know","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"which factors are going to make a difference .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"But I have no doubt","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"that it had some impact ,","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"just based on the coverage . \"","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"In the NPR interview , Obama expressed incredulity at Republican party support for Trump ' s foreign policy positions ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"which have been uniformly supportive of Russian president Vladimir Putin .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"\" This is somebody ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"the former head of the KGB ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"who is responsible for crushing democracy in Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"muzzling the press ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"throwing political dissidents in jail ,","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"countering American efforts","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"to expand freedom at every turn ;","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"is currently making decisions","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that ' s leading to a slaughter in Syria , \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"the outgoing president said .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"\" And a big chunk of the Republican party ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"which prided itself during the Reagan era and for decades","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"that followed","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"as being the bulwark against Russian influence ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"now suddenly is embracing him . \"","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Earlier on Thursday , the White House went its furthest yet","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"in joining the dots between Trump and Putin .","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"Press secretary Josh Earnest pointed reporters to a unanimous statement from all 17 intelligence agencies ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"issued in October ,","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"that found","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"\" only Russia ' s senior-most officials could have authorized these activities \" .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"The press secretary said","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that in his personal view , that sentence was \" not intended to be subtle \" ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"that it was \" pretty obvious that they were referring to the senior-most government official in Russia \" .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Ben Rhodes , Obama ' s deputy national security adviser for strategic communications , agreed .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"things happen in the Russian government of this consequence","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"without Vladimir Putin knowing about it , \"","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"he told MSNBC .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"But Russian foreign minister Sergei Lavrov told state TV channel Rossiya-24","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"he was \" dumbstruck \" by the reports of Putin ' s alleged involvement .","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"this is just silly ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"and the futility","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"of the attempt","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"to convince somebody of this","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"is absolutely obvious , \"","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Putin ' s spokesman Dmitry Peskov said on Friday of the hacking accusation","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"that the US should \" either stop talking about it","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"or finally produce some evidence ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"otherwise it all begins to look unseemly \" .","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"The White House said","depth":3},{"id":130,"text":"Obama would hold a press conference in Washington on Friday at 2.15pm ET","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"( 7.15pm GMT )","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"before leaving for his annual family vacation in Hawaii .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":233,"right":264,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":233,"left":207,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":135,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":134,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":155,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":142,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration",